high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn left at the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Move a bit to the left
Slice the tomato on the table
Turn left, go to the basket on the floor
Put the knife in the basket
Turn left, go to the table, turn right
Pick up a tomato slice from the table
Turn right, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn right and go to the stove
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Turn right, go forward, turn right, go forward, turn left and go to the basket
Put the tomato slice in the basket
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, cook a slice

high_descs: Turn right then head to the right side of the round table
Pick up the bread knife on the round table
Turn left make a step then face the middle tomato
Slice the tomato
Turn left then head to the trash bin
Put the bread knife in the trash bin
Turn left then head to the round table
Pick up a slice of tomato on the table
Turn left and head to the microwave above the stove
Open the microwave and put in and out the slice tomato
Turn right then head to the trash bin
Put the slice tomato in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the warm slice tomato in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right after passing the end of the counter on the right, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the table.
Take the knife to the left of the large spoon on the table.
Go a step to the left, face the table.
Cut the tomato next to the cup on the table into slices.
Turn left, go forward to the wall to the right of the trash bin. Turn left to face the trash bin.
Put the knife in the trash bin.
Turn left, go forward, turn left at the round table.
Take a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn left after passing the counter on the left, go forward and to the left to the stove top.
Cook the tomato in the microwave above the stove top. Take the tomato from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward past the end of the counter, turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left to face the trash bin.
Put the tomato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in a trash bin.
